  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed; the assessment team concluded that the body of evidence, taken together, supports acceptance of the model for the stated context of use. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all five flow-speed combinations and hemolysis predictions remained below the absolute clinical threshold with adequate margin.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-vad-hemolysis-accepted",
